'''Winter Wrap Up'''是一首由[[小马镇]]全体小马演唱的[[歌曲]]。这首歌出现于[[我的小马驹：友谊就是魔法]]第一季的[[冬季清扫|同名剧集]]中。其部分片段在剧集放送一个月之前就已经在Youtube上发布。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mylittleponynews.com/2010/12/winter-wrap-up-on-youtube-again.html|title=My Little Pony News reporting on the leak|date=2010-11-24|accessdate=2013-05-03}}</ref>

==制作与二次使用==
本歌作为[[家庭媒体#一区|DVD]]《My Little Pony Friendship is Magic: A Pony For Every Season》中一首跟唱歌曲发行，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.familyfriendlygaming.com/Reviews/2013/My%20Little%20Pony%20Friendship%20is%20Magic%20A%20Pony%20For%20Every%20Season.html|title=My Little Pony Friendship is Magic A Pony For Every Season - Family Friendly Gaming Review|date=2013-11-05|accessdate=2013-11-11}}</ref>且在[[wikipedia:Chuck E. Cheese's|出奇老鼠]]电子动画展的幕间休息时播放，在[[Treehouse Live! My Little Pony|My Little Pony Live Show]]中也有收录。

Instrumental versions of this song play during Twilight's organized wrap up in [[Winter Wrap Up|the same episode]], during the [[Commercials#Show|character profile]] compilation on the [[Home media#Early and promotional variants|DVD]] ''My Little Pony Friendship is Magic: Applebuck Season'', and during the [[Merchandise#Software|interactive storybook]] ''Twilight Sparkle: Teacher for a Day'' and its Ruckus Reader version ''Twilight Sparkle's Special Lesson''.

[[Discord]] briefly sings the song's chorus in [[Princess Twilight Sparkle - Part 1]] and [[Pinkie Pie]] briefly uses the melody from the song for "Fruit Bat Roundup" in [[Bats!]]; in the [[IDW comics]], [[Rarity]], [[Dr. Hooves]], and [[Fluttershy]] briefly sing a "Summer Wrap-Up" counterpart of the song on {{comic|10}} page 22 and a line of the song appears on {{comic|20}} page 18. It is the eighth track on the [[Songs of Friendship and Magic]] soundtrack album. It also serves as the first of two bonus tracks of side B on the Luna variant of the vinyl album [[Magical Friendship Tour]]. In the soundtrack album [[Songs of Harmony]], the song is featured in an [[True True Friend Winter Wrap-Up|ultimate mash-up]] with the [[Magical Mystery Cure|season three finale]] song [[A True, True Friend]], including vocals by [[Bronies|brony]] musician [[w:c:mlpfanart:BlackGryph0n|Gabriel Brown]]. It also serves as the sixth track on the [[My Little Pony 2015 Convention Collection]].

